  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t在openAI的刻意限制下，对于任何涉及政治”争议“的具体话题，chatGPT通常会极力避免给出明确答案，其回复一般是和稀泥式的官僚辞令。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n但是如果我们去掉具体的名字，AI就会给出诚实的回答。判断某国的主张和依据是否legit。<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>历史上有记载，就等于拥有“自古以来的主权”？</b><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLnBvc3RpbWcuY2MvWnEwTFpUcm4vMjAyMzAyMTktMTUxNy5qcGc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Zq0LZTrn/20230219-1517.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Zq0LZTrn/20230219-1517.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Zq0LZTrn/20230219-1517.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>古代海防图能否构成</b><b>领土占有的意思或者实际控制的依据</b><b>？</b><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLnBvc3RpbWcuY2MvMTMwenQ2clkvMjAyMzAyMTktMTUyNS5qcGc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.postimg.cc/130zt6rY/20230219-1525.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.postimg.cc/130zt6rY/20230219-1525.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/130zt6rY/20230219-1525.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLnBvc3RpbWcuY2MvVjV5alltTFEvMjAyMzAyMTktMTQ0MmNvYXN0YWxkZWZlbnNlY2hhcnQuanBn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.postimg.cc/V5yjYmLQ/20230219-1442coastaldefensechart.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.postimg.cc/V5yjYmLQ/20230219-1442coastaldefensechart.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/V5yjYmLQ/20230219-1442coastaldefensechart.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n最后再来个事实检查<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLnBvc3RpbWcuY2MvTXB2cDBUVnovMjAyMzAyMTktMTQyN2ZhY3RjaGVjay5qcGc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Mpvp0TVz/20230219-1427factcheck.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Mpvp0TVz/20230219-1427factcheck.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Mpvp0TVz/20230219-1427factcheck.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLnBvc3RpbWcuY2MvM0pnZ01ucjcvMTEyMjM3OTYtMTY1NTQ2ODg0NDY5ODc5OC03OTQwNzk0OTE1ODk0Nzg1MjU4LW4uanBn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.postimg.cc/3JggMnr7/11223796-1655468844698798-7940794915894785258-n.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.postimg.cc/3JggMnr7/11223796-1655468844698798-7940794915894785258-n.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/3JggMnr7/11223796-1655468844698798-7940794915894785258-n.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
